# Vegas Royale Slot Machine Game - Real-Time Chat System

This project integrates a real-time chat system with the Vegas Royale Slot machine game, allowing players to interact and share their experiences in real-time.

## Features
- **Real-Time Messaging**: Players can send and receive messages instantly.
- **User Authentication**: Secure user login for personalized chat experiences.
- **Game Notifications**: Alerts for in-game events sent to chat.
- **Emoji Support**: Users can express themselves with emojis.

## Technologies Used
- WebSockets for real-time communication
- Node.js for the server-side logic
- React.js for the front-end interface

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository.
2. Install dependencies using `npm install`.
3. Run the server with `node server.js`.
4. Open the client in your browser.

## Usage
- Join the chat while playing the Vegas Royale Slot machine to interact with other players.
- Report any issues or suggestions via the support channel in the chat.

Happy gaming!